<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_219" id="109r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_219_r1l2">Hanſen <expan>vviſentaw<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l3">cʒum Newenhaws</ab>
</del></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_219_r1l4"><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vvÿſentaw<ex>er</ex></expan> / vns hat fürgelegt / <expan>h<ex>er</ex></expan> Hans Capplan <expan>cʒu<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>heilıg<ex>en</ex></expan> Krewtʒ beÿ vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l5">der vns cʒu verſprechen ſtet / vvie Jr <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Armeman</expan> cʒu Aichenſtutt auf <expan>ſeıne<ex>m</ex></expan> gut </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l6">daʒ ſein mit gevvalt <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd hinvveg gefürt habt / vnd nie keins <expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l7">Jm begert habt / das vns cʒemal 
<del rend="strikethrough">frewn </del> fremd von ew dünckt / vnd begern <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l8">antvvurt <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒevviſen / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> / </ab>
</del>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_219" id="109r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><del rend="crossout">Hansen <expan>Wisentaw<ex>er</ex></expan> czum
                            Newenhaws </del></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><del rend="crossout"><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Wysentaw<ex>er</ex></expan>, uns hat fürgelegt
                                    <expan>h<ex>er</ex></expan> Hans, capplan
                                <expan>czu<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>heilig<ex>en</ex></expan> krewcz bey uns, der uns czu versprechen
                            stet, wie ir <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>armeman</expan> czu Aichenstutt auf
                                <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> gut daz sein mit gewalt
                                    <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> und hinweg gefürt habt und nie
                            keins <expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan> von im begert habt, das uns czemal
                            fremd von ew dünckt, und begern <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> antwurt
                                    <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> czewisen.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                            <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>.</del></ab>
</div>
</div></body>
